mationEvent</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>CSSCharsetRule</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSCounterStyleRule\"><code>CSSCounterStyleRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSFontFaceRule\"><code>CSSFontFaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>CSSFontFeatureValuesMap</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>CSSFontFeatureValuesRule</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSImportRule\"><code>CSSImportRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>CSSMarginRule</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>CSSVariablesMap</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>CSSViewportRule</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/style\"><code>ElementCSSInlineStyle</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>GeometryUtils</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>GetStyleUtils</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLLinkElement\"><code>LinkStyle</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaList\"><code>MediaList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>PseudoElement</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Several other interfaces are also extended by the CSSOM-related specifications: <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLImageElement\"><code>HTMLImageElement</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a>, and <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"tutorials","title":"Tutorials","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model/Determining_the_dimensions_of_elements\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Determining the dimensions of elements (en-US)</a> (it needs some updating as it was made in the DHTML/Ajax era).</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model/Managing_screen_orientation\">Managing screen orientation</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/","title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/","title":"CSSOM View Module"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.css-houdini.org/css-typed-om/","title":"CSS Typed OM Level 2"}],"query":"undefined"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility_notes","title":"Browser compatibility notes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>All these features have been added little by little over the years to the different browsers: it was a quite complex process that can't be summarized in a simple table. Please refer to the specific interfaces for its availability.</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Reference","id":"reference"},{"text":"Tutorials","id":"tutorials"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility notes","id":"browser_compatibility_notes"}],"summary":"The CSS Object Model is a set of APIs allowing to manipulate CSS from JavaScript. It is the pendant of DOM and HTML APIs, but for CSS. It allows to read and modify CSS style dynamically.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSS Object Model","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"CSS Object Model","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSS オブジェクトモデル (CSSOM)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSS 객체 모델 (CSSOM)","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"CSS Object Model","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSS Object Model","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/css_object_model","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/css_object_model/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model","title":"CSS Object Model"}],"pageTitle":"CSS Object Model - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}